result.title: CodeCraft 2015 Replay
result.content:
You might remember the original contest(http://codeforces.com/blog/entry/15810 ).
We decided to keep a replay of contest on GYM, so that problems(and tutorials) can be easily uploaded for practice later on.

It's of duration 5 hours and consists of 11 problems ranging from cakewalk to hard.
Link to gym contet: http://codeforces.com/gym/100589
It'll start at 1400 hrs IST. Time in other zones: http://bit.ly/1wBNkwb

Happy Coding!
